short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension saves all open tabs to a batch file

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension saves all open tabs in the current Google Chrome window into a batch file that can be used to open the same tabs again. If the "Open Tabs In New Window" option is set, the tabs will be opened in a new Google Chrome window. If the "Open Incognito Window" option is set, the tabs will be opened in an incognito window.
